Package com.ibm.wala.ssa.analysis

Class ExplodedControlFlowGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.wala.ssa.analysis.ExplodedControlFlowGraph
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ControlFlowGraph<SSAInstruction,​IExplodedBasicBlock>, MinimalCFG<IExplodedBasicBlock>, EdgeManager<IExplodedBasicBlock>, Graph<IExplodedBasicBlock>, NodeManager<IExplodedBasicBlock>, NumberedEdgeManager<IExplodedBasicBlock>, NumberedGraph<IExplodedBasicBlock>, NumberedNodeManager<IExplodedBasicBlock>, java.lang.Iterable<IExplodedBasicBlock>
    public class ExplodedControlFlowGraph
extends java.lang.Object
implements ControlFlowGraph<SSAInstruction,​IExplodedBasicBlock>
    A view of a control flow graph where each basic block corresponds to exactly one SSA instruction index.

    Prototype: Not terribly efficient.
